b58c12f797","tid":2327351,"uid":128369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T06:41:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T06:46:18.000Z","msg":"唔係 你同我都睇緊既連登仲係有人share佢啲post"},{"pid":"b7b5eef4d9042a56670a06722dd7c247537cab6c","tid":2327351,"uid":37396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T06:47:17.000Z","msg":"講到民建聯無共產黨資助咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ab1c6d4f9ea6056b2a244d56d1c7fab5b25e7a7","tid":2327351,"uid":158074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T06:49:37.000Z","msg":"民主黨，公民黨係唔合法組織？如果合洗，捐錢比佢哋犯咗邊條例？"},{"pid":"8a466ae854d3de6c3685058759f7ff0834a2fc66","tid":2327351,"uid":12186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T07:00:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"20715bb3069d2841a40f92aefb88feece877b026","tid":2327351,"uid":171107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"19ab0222de54933e5231882dcd9cc44090799a8e","tid":2327351,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T04:11:21.000Z","msg":"全國政協副主席梁振英15日晚在社交媒體發文，引用「壹傳媒股民」披露的數據，揭露正在監獄服刑的亂港頭目黎智英多年來資助支持反中亂港政黨與骨幹的具體情況。其中民主黨、公民黨五年間合共獲得黎智英近3000萬港元的巨額捐款。<br />\n<br />\n　另外，打著宗教旗號積極從事反中亂港陰謀活動的陳日君收到黎智英2000萬港元。<br />\n<br />\n　梁振英在帖文中寫到：除了我三天前臚列「壹傳媒股民」揭露的捐款、貸款和其他捐贈外，2011年10月，「FOXY洩密」亦揭露黎智英由2005年至2011年共捐出的53筆政治獻金，當中包括：<br />\n<br />\n　1.民主黨於2006年至2011年，合共收受黎智英11筆共1,504萬港元。<br />\n<br />\n　2.公民黨於2006年至2011年，合共收受黎智英12筆共1456.65萬港元。<br />\n<br />\n　3.陳方安生於2007至2009年，合共收受黎智英3筆共130萬港元。<br />\n<br />\n　4.「前綫」於2007至2008年，合共收受黎智英2筆共40萬港元。<br />\n<br />\n　5.陳日君主教，於2005年至2010年，合共收受黎智英6筆共2000萬港元。<br />\n<br />\n　6.劉勝義神父(Father John Russell) 於2006至2011年，合共收受黎智英6筆共150萬港元。<br />\n<br />\n　7.南耀寧神父(Father Yves Nalet, 自1984年擔任天主教耶穌會中華省的耶穌會刊物《中國消息分析》《China News Analysis》主編，1996年移居台灣，每周編撰對內地的新聞分析) ，2009年至2011年，合共收受黎智英3筆共300萬台幣。<br />\n<br />\n　8.劉裕政總主教(Eugene M. Nugent , 2000年教廷駐香港代辦，現任駐馬達加斯加大使)，於2006年11月9日收受黎智英50萬港元。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.hkcd.com/userfiles/1608089792.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcd.com%2Fuserfiles%2F1608089792.jpg&h=c1f024d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（fb)<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">http://www.hkcd .com/content/2020-12/16/content_1236277.html</code></pre>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T07:00:52.000Z","msg":"捐款有咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你老母支那人食香大"},{"pid":"307b34ee15c5d61a3e5cbc116e33d1ce6107f89e","tid":2327351,"uid":256246,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T07:01:59.000Z","msg":"係咪就係ugl果5000萬？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24f24c0868725fe67456c0da08c6daf7ae5734f7","tid":2327351,"uid":318720,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"90c10440333f451b646e8e8dda8a8babef8d1b75","tid":2327351,"uid":17281,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T04:38:27.000Z","msg":"黎生原來真係做左咁多野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T07:06:59.000Z","msg":"萍果都係蝕住做"}]}